channel.title: 317 server with 508 textures
channel.description:
[b]There! I am back and made something again. Berky-Scape supports a 317 server with 508 decorates![/b] Some pics quickly cuz I have to go!
[IMG]http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/6475/housedeco.png[/img] [IMG]http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/1544/decoratives.png[/img] [IMG]http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/4668/apedeco.png[/img] [IMG]http://img29.imageshack.us/img29/7496/treedeco.png[/img]
Did you enjoy them? More coming soon, I also fixed the Lava in the wilderniss.
Credits: The guy in client hacks who posted textures. Berky for adding them in the server correctly. Took like half hour.
